salixProductPlugInMIB.name: salixProductPlugInMIB
salixProductPlugInMIB.contactinfo: 904 Wind River Lane Suite 101 Gaithersburg, MD 20878 (301)-417-0017
salixProductPlugInMIB.description: The MIB describing SALIX specific extensions to the M4-MIB

SalixPlugInUnitType.name: SalixPlugInUnitType
SalixPlugInUnitType.description: HNE hardware plug-in unit types: unknown(0) - Unknown plug-in unit type mpu(1) - Management Processor Unit dpu(2) - Data Processor Unit smu(3) - Sync Module Unit liu(4) - Line Interface Unit hsf(5) - Hybrid Switch Fabric Unit powerSupply(6) - Power supply fan(7) - Fan Unit hardDrive(8) - Hard drive xcoder(9) - Transcoder ds3Liu(10) - Ds3 LIU softwarePacketLiu(11) - Software Packet LIU packetLiu(12)

salixPlugInUnitDpuTable.name: salixPlugInUnitDpuTable
salixPlugInUnitDpuTable.description: The HNE Data Processor Unit (DPU) plug-in unit table.

salixPlugInUnitDpuEntry.name: salixPlugInUnitDpuEntry
salixPlugInUnitDpuEntry.description: An entry in the HNE DPU plug-in unit table. An entry contains HNE specific plug-in information for a Data Processor Unit. This table parallels the salixAtmfM4PlugInUnitTable. However, only valid LIU indices of the salixAtmfM4PlugInUnitTable will contain information pertinent to a DPU.

salixDpuProcessorType.name: salixDpuProcessorType
salixDpuProcessorType.description: The type of processor installed on the Data Processor Unit. mipsR4700(1) - MIPS R4700 RISC processor.

salixPlugInUnitLiuTable.name: salixPlugInUnitLiuTable
salixPlugInUnitLiuTable.description: The HNE Line Interface Unit (LIU) plug-in unit table.

salixPlugInUnitLiuEntry.name: salixPlugInUnitLiuEntry
salixPlugInUnitLiuEntry.description: An entry in the HNE LIU plug-in unit table. An entry contains HNE specific plug-in information for an LIU. This table is indexed the same as the salixAtmfM4PlugInUnitTable. However, only valid LIU indices of the salixAtmfM4PlugInUnitTable will contain information pertinent to an LIU.

salixLiuOrderwireEnabled.name: salixLiuOrderwireEnabled
salixLiuOrderwireEnabled.description: Indication of whether the orderwire is enabled. true(1) - the orderwire is enabled false(2) - the orderwire is not-enabled

salixLiuOrderwireSonetLine.name: salixLiuOrderwireSonetLine
salixLiuOrderwireSonetLine.description: Identifies which of the SONET lines on the plug-in unit to take the orderwire from for drop to the handset.

salixLiuOrderwireSonetLayer.name: salixLiuOrderwireSonetLayer
salixLiuOrderwireSonetLayer.description: Identifies which of the two orderwire signals in the selected SONET line should be routed to the handset on the plug-in unit.

salixPlugInUnitSyncTable.name: salixPlugInUnitSyncTable
salixPlugInUnitSyncTable.description: The HNE Sync module plug-in unit table.

salixPlugInUnitSyncEntry.name: salixPlugInUnitSyncEntry
salixPlugInUnitSyncEntry.description: An entry in the HNE Sync module plug-in unit table. An entry contains HNE specific plug-in information for a Sync module. This table is indexed the same as the salixAtmfM4PlugInUnitTable. However, only valid Sync module indices of the salixAtmfM4PlugInUnitTable will contain information pertinent to a Sync module.

salixSyncSlotIdentifier.name: salixSyncSlotIdentifier
salixSyncSlotIdentifier.description: Indicates whether the Sync module is installed in the primary or secondary plug-in unit slot.

salixPlugInUnitXcdrEntry.name: salixPlugInUnitXcdrEntry
salixPlugInUnitXcdrEntry.description: An entry in the XCDR table. On entry exists for each Transcoder in the system. Each entry contains information and configuration about the Transcoder

salixPlugInUnitXcdrPercentWorkingDsp.name: salixPlugInUnitXcdrPercentWorkingDsp
salixPlugInUnitXcdrPercentWorkingDsp.description: Represents the percentage of the Dsp's on the Transcoder that are currently working. The exact Dsp's that have failed can be found in the itxDspConfigTable from the SALIX-ITX-MIB

salixPlugInUnitXcdrType.name: salixPlugInUnitXcdrType
salixPlugInUnitXcdrType.description: This object describes the Type of Transcoder described by the entry. voipServer(1) - A Transcoder that is limited to VOIP calls toneAndAnnouncementServer(2) - A Transcoder that is limited to announcements and tones universalServer(3) - A Transcoder that can do both Annoucements and VOIP calls

salixPlugInUnitDs3LiuTable.name: salixPlugInUnitDs3LiuTable
salixPlugInUnitDs3LiuTable.description: The DS3 Line Interface Unit (DS3LIU) plug-in unit table.

salixPlugInUnitDs3LiuEntry.name: salixPlugInUnitDs3LiuEntry
salixPlugInUnitDs3LiuEntry.description: An entry in the SALIX Ds3Liu Plugin Unit Table. One entry exists for each DS3LIU in the system, and contains information specific to DS3LIUs.

salixDs3LiuGroupNumber.name: salixDs3LiuGroupNumber
salixDs3LiuGroupNumber.description: The group that the DS3LIU corresponding to this entry belongs to. Valid groups are numbered from 1 to 4. A value of 0 indicates that the DS3LIU does not belong in a group.

salixPPICompliance.name: salixPPICompliance
salixPPICompliance.description: The basic implementation requirements for the SALIX-M4-MIB.
